
This app is for using Lenovo Yoga in tablet mode on Linux.
It turn on/off input devices. You can edit this list in ./tabletMode.py

Intalling
  To use it you need to have Python2 and kivy library. For installing them:
  $ sudo apt-get install python2.7
  $ sudo add-apt-repository ppa:kivy-team/kivy
  $ sudo apt-get update
  $ sudo apt-get install python-kiv

Using:  
  Go into the dir with app
  $ ./tabletMode.py 
